sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Application
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Storage as PVC/Database<br/>5432/3306/TCP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraper

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: Model Prediction Monitoring

    User->>KServe: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token TLS1.2+
    KServe->>TrustyAI: Forward Prediction (Payload Processor)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 80-443
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Store Prediction Data<br/>Filesystem or DB (TLS conditional)
    TrustyAI-->>KServe: ACK
    KServe-->>User: Prediction Response<br/>JSON HTTPS

    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 (Internal)
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: Metrics (Explainability, Bias)

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: OAuth-Protected Access

    User->>Route: GET /api/endpoint<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    Route->>OAuth: Forward Request<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS1.2+
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth Token<br/>OpenShift SAR
    OAuth->>TrustyAI: Forward Authenticated Request<br/>HTTP/8080
    TrustyAI-->>OAuth: Response
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: HTTPS Response

    participant LMUser as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant LMCtrl as LMEvalJob Controller
    participant Kueue as Kueue<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMPod as LMES Pod
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over LMUser,S3: Flow 3: LM Evaluation Job

    LMUser->>K8sAPI: kubectl create -f lmevaljob.yaml<br/>HTTPS/6443 Bearer Token TLS1.3
    K8sAPI->>LMCtrl: Watch Event: LMEvalJob Created
    LMCtrl->>Kueue: Create Workload<br/>HTTPS/6443 SA Token TLS1.3
    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Admit Workload<br/>HTTPS/6443 SA Token
    K8sAPI->>LMPod: Schedule Pod<br/>lm-evaluation-harness
    LMPod->>HF: Download Model/Dataset<br/>HTTPS/443 API Token TLS1.2+
    LMPod->>KServe: Evaluate Model<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token TLS1.2+
    KServe-->>LMPod: Inference Results
    LMPod->>S3: Store Evaluation Results<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM TLS1.2+
    LMPod-->>K8sAPI: Job Complete

    participant Client as External Client
    participant GWRoute as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GWOAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Guardrails as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8032/TCP HTTPS
    participant Detector as Detector InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Generator as Generator InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Generator: Flow 4: Guardrails Request Processing

    Client->>GWRoute: POST /generate<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    GWRoute->>GWOAuth: OAuth Redirect<br/>HTTPS/8443 Bearer Token
    GWOAuth->>Guardrails: Authenticated Request<br/>HTTPS/8032 TLS (service-ca)
    Guardrails->>Detector: Check Input Safety<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token TLS1.2+
    Detector-->>Guardrails: Safety Score
    Guardrails->>Generator: Generate Response<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token TLS1.2+
    Generator-->>Guardrails: Generated Text
    Guardrails->>Detector: Check Output Safety<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token TLS1.2+
    Detector-->>Guardrails: Safety Score
    Guardrails-->>GWOAuth: Filtered Response
    GWOAuth-->>GWRoute: Response
    GWRoute-->>Client: HTTPS Response
